  <條文>
    <條號>Article 66</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Regulations on election and recall of elected personnel, personnel management, and disposal of financial affairs of civil associations shall be prescribed by the central regulating authority.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 67</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Act shall become effective as of the date of promulgation.
The articles of this law amended on 12th May of 2009 of the Republic of China take effect on 23rd November of 2009.
]]></條文內容>
